Global Industrial Grade Propionic Acid Market Insights
Industrial Grade Propionic Acid Market size was valued at USD 1.45 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.10 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Industrial Grade Propionic Acid Market Overview
The global industrial grade propionic acid market is expected to reach USD 2.5 billion by 2028, growing at a CAGR of 5.3% from 2021 to 2028. The market is driven by the increasing demand for propionic acid in various industries such as agriculture, food preservation, and chemical manufacturing. The growing need for propionic acid as a preservative and antimicrobial agent in livestock feed and food products is fueling its growth. The market is also expanding due to the increasing application of propionic acid in the production of various chemicals, plastics, and herbicides. The Asia-Pacific region holds the largest market share, followed by North America and Europe due to the rising industrial activities in these regions.

